OL,3,CAnnemarie Jacir's Palestine 36 retells
OL,4,Ccountry's erased anti-colonial history
OL,6,FThe film follows the events of the
OL,7,F1936`1939 Arab revolt in Palestine
OL,8,Fagainst British colonialism
OL,10,FWhen we meet, I ask acclaimed
OL,11,Ffilmmaker Annemarie Jacir about her
OL,12,Fposition as a woman in Palestine
OL,13,Fmaking films.
OL,15,FShe gets asked this a lot and responds
OL,16,Fby saying there are actually many Arab
OL,17,Fwomen who are making movies.
