OL,3,CAnnemarie Jacir's Palestine 36 retells
OL,4,Ccountry's erased anti-colonial history
OL,6,FHer focus in her new film is the Arab
OL,7,Frevolt against British colonial rule
OL,8,Fin Palestine beginning in 1936. That
OL,9,Fthe empire extended here is something
OL,10,Fshe would like everyone to know, and
OL,11,Fshe fears it is a period of history
OL,12,Fthat has effectively been erased.
