OL,6,FJacir's film has been chosen as
OL,7,FPalestine's Oscars entry, her fourth
OL,8,Ffilm to be chosen in her career.
OL,10,FBut for her, more importantly, talking
OL,11,Fabout the history of Palestine gives
OL,12,Fpeople, particularly today, a better
OL,13,Funderstanding of what is happening in
OL,14,Fthe region now.
